movie.title: Gone with the Wind
movie.plot: The spoiled daughter of a well-to-do plantation owner is forced to use every means at her disposal to claw her way out of poverty, following Maj. Gen. William Sherman's destructive "March to the Sea,‚Äù during the American Civil War.
